description:
The Marine Plant, a company  that cultivates underwater algae, ask  the "Alfa Agency " to locate some robot , deprived of the first law of robotics, which could harm the workers who work in the deep seabed . 
Nathan , Jack O'Ryan and Sigmund are sent to the "Sea One" station to investigate , but they  suspect that the cultivation of algae is a cover for drug trafficking . 
Meanwhile, Douglas Martin ,of " the Marine Plant" , discovers the true intentions of the agents and prepares an act of sabotage.
name: Paura sul Fondo
i morbosi vizi del professor hammer

description:
In the palace of Skotos, a creature obtained by the genetic codes of Skotos and Gabriel, called Element X, tries to free his destructive energy.

Meanwhile Nathan, along with Janine, went to see Ann, that saw in a dream ordering him to search for Raven and eliminate it.

Nathan, along with Jack, April, May, Legs and Link attacks "Apokalipse Plaza", the building of Skotos, in order to kill Raven.

While Nathan, with the help of the telepathic Ann, faces Raven, Jack finds himself face to face with Skotos and the truth about his obscure past.
name: Il Ritorno Di Raven

description:
Olga , the girlfriend of the robot of "Link " , shows no sign of her for some days. Link , Nathan and May  ask to Hashimoto the permission to do research in the Valley of the Dinosaurs .
While the agents are on the road, Hashimoto was commissioned  by Yabuno to prevent the access to the valley to everyone : then , with the airplane driven by him , Reiko and Tochiro , will enter in orbit in order to destroy the valley . 
In the meantime, Nathan , Link and May entered the valley, where they found Olga , Ran , and Minako Fujiwara .
name: Il Satellite Killer

description: First Korky cover drawn by Charles Grigg.

As a result of  the disappearance of the seventeen year old "Lynn Deckar"d , which manifested ESP powers, Nathan Never is charged by her parents
to find their daughter .
He starts to follow the trails of Rick Sheldon, Lynn 's ex-boyfriend , Nathan finds him dead , killed by a stranger , sent by Dr. " Queenstain " a  programmer of the " Eclipse ", a video game company .
Meanwhile, the hacker Derek Jordan , after receiving a tip-off on the Shady trades of  Eclipse , receives also a mysterious mail with a request for help.
name: Progetto Mortale
